command.joinmsg.description:
Set a join message for new joined users
If you want to reset your message to default, just type ``s+joinmsg <Channel>``
If you want to disable your event, use ``s+joinmsg delete``
User Mention: {user}
Guild Name: {guild}

command.leavemsg.description:
Set a leave message for users who left the servers
If you want to reset your message to default, just type ``s+leavemsg <Channel>``
If you want to disable your event, use ``s+leavemsg delete``
User Mention: {user}
Guild Name: {guild}
